          "Left Join on RealCID+DateID. AUM has one row per customer per day."
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "01f137da54601959afb5a85aa742c486",
        "left": {
          "identifier": "main.etoro_kpi.vg_customer_customer_first_dates",
          "alias": "vg_customer_customer_first_dates"
        },
        "right": {
          "identifier": "main.etoro_kpi.customer_snapshot_v",
          "alias": "customer_snapshot_v"
        },
        "sql": [
          "`vg_customer_customer_first_dates`.`RealCID` = `customer_snapshot_v`.`RealCID`",
          "--rt=FROM_RELATIONSHIP_TYPE_ONE_TO_MANY--"
        ],
        "instruction": [
          "oin on RealCID only (one-to-many: one row per customer in first dates, many snapshot rows by day). Always set customer_snapshot_v.DateID: Yesterday for “current” attributes; explicit = / BETWEEN / IN for history — not MAX(DateID). Use first dates for milestone dates; use snapshot for as-of-day attributes. "
        ]
      }
